name: Traffic Control (V)
Lore: 'Expert traffic controllers coordinate launches faster than automated launch systems. Rebel bases scramble fighters quickly during Imperial attacks.',
Text: 'Plays on table. ''Three'' on An Unusual Amount Of Fear is treated as ''Four''. You lose no Force to Boonta Eve Podrace. Opponent''s retrieval from Boonta Eve Podrace may not be canceled. While you occupy three battlegrounds, Watto''s Box is suspended.',
